name: Deep Trouble
description:
Oh no! Planet Purpura is in deep trouble. The Ranger tries to look for treasure guarded by a Kraken. But, now, The Kraken has awakened. Can The Ranger survived? or this is a doomsday for Planet Purpura?

This piece is a 2nd piece of series "Purpura". Hope all of you enjoy my artworks. Thank you
